      <description>&lt;section id="overview" data-observe="true"                         class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_175px] sm-opaque1 py-5 px-5 lg:py-10 lg:px-10 pt-24 lg:pt-10 mb-0 lg:mb-10"&gt;                          &lt;div class=""&gt;                             &lt;h2 class="font-serif font-bold tracking-wide uppercase text-2xl text-cardforeground"&gt;                                 Overview                                                               &lt;/h2&gt;                              &lt;div                                 class="overview-icons mt-8 grid gap-4 xl:gap-6 grid-cols-1 xl:grid-cols-2 pr-8 text-cardforeground"&gt;                                 &lt;div class="release-date" style="grid-column: 1 / -1;"&gt;                                     &lt;div class="flex min-w-0 gap-x-6 items-center justify-center"&gt;                                         &lt;div&gt;&lt;i class="fa-light fa-headphones"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;                                         &lt;div class="min-w-0 flex-auto"&gt;                                             &lt;p                                                 class="uppercase font-bold  text-xs tracking-widest text-subheader font-serif"&gt;                                                 Releasing on                                             &lt;/p&gt;                                             &lt;p class="text-sm"&gt;                                                 Thursday, May 15, 2025                                            &lt;/p&gt;                                         &lt;/div&gt;                                     &lt;/div&gt;                                 &lt;/div&gt;                                                                                                    &lt;div class="flex min-w-0 gap-x-6 items-center justify-center"&gt;                                     &lt;div&gt;&lt;i class="icon fa-light fa-typewriter text-center"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;          